            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice the <strong>ciabatta rolls</strong> into thin slices</p>\n<p>Add the <strong>slices</strong> to a tray and drizzle them with <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt </strong></p>\n<p>Put the tray in the oven and cook for 5-8 min or until crisp and golden – these are your <strong>crostini</strong></p>",
